== 製作 ==
=== 開發 ===
2013年7月30日，《[[綠箭俠_(電視劇)|綠箭俠]]》電視劇開創者[[葛瑞格·貝蘭提|葛瑞格·貝蘭提]]和{{le|安德魯·克瑞斯伯格|Andrew Kreisberg}}、《綠箭俠》試播集導演[[戴維·納特|戴維·納特]]以及[[DC漫畫|DC漫畫]]的創意總監[[傑夫·強斯|傑夫·強斯]]將基於漫畫角色[[閃電俠_(貝瑞·艾倫)|「閃電俠」貝瑞·艾倫]]開發影集，講述貝瑞·艾倫成為閃電俠的起源故事<ref name="DeadlineAnnouncement">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2013/07/cw-eyes-flash-series-with-arrows-greg-berlanti-andrew-kreisberg-david-nutter/ |title=CW Eyes 'Flash' Series With 'Arrow's Greg Berlanti, Andrew Kreisberg & David Nutter |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |website=Deadline Hollywood |date=2013-07-30 |access-date=2013-07-30 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130801015113/http://www.deadline.com/2013/07/cw-eyes-flash-series-with-arrows-greg-berlanti-andrew-kreisberg-david-nutter/ |archive-date=2013-08-01 |language=en-US}}</ref>。安德魯·克瑞斯伯格透露貝瑞·艾倫將以常設角色首先出演於影集《綠箭俠》第二季的其中三集，均由貝蘭提、克瑞斯伯格和強斯執筆編劇，最後一集作為《閃電俠》的[[電視試播|後門試播集]]<ref name="THRJuly2013">{{cite magazine|url=https://hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/flash-writers-preview-cws-newest-595705 |title='Flash' Writers Preview the CW's Newest Superhero |last=Goldberg |first=Lesley |magazine=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2013-07-30 |access-date=2013-07-30 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130801185107/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/flash-writers-preview-cws-newest-595705 |archive-date=2013-08-01 |language=en-US}}</ref>。貝瑞在正式播出的《綠箭俠》第二季中出現兩集，CW電視網取消製作後門試播集，以傳統的試播集替代，這給了製作組更多預算，同時可以專注於講述貝瑞的故事線。2014年1月29日，CW電視網宣佈預訂該試播集，編劇包括貝蘭提、克瑞斯伯格和強斯，導演為戴維·納特<ref name="DeadlinePilot">{{cite web|url=https://www.deadline.com/2013/11/cws-the-flash-to-do-standalone-pilot-instead-of-arrow-backdoor-pilot-episode/ |title=CW’s ‘The Flash’ To Do Stand-Alone Pilot Instead Of ‘Arrow’ Backdoor Pilot Episode |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |date=2013-11-18 |access-date=2013-11-18 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131119211413/http://www.deadline.com/2013/11/cws-the-flash-to-do-standalone-pilot-instead-of-arrow-backdoor-pilot-episode/ |archive-date=2013-11-19 |language=en-US}}</ref><ref name="PilotOrdered">{{cite magazine|last=Goldberg |first=Lesley |title='Supernatural' Spinoff, Rob Thomas' 'iZombie,' 'Flash' Ordered to Pilot at CW |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/supernatural-spinoff-rob-thomas-izombie-675484 |magazine=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2014-01-29 |access-date=2014-01-29 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140301182716/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/supernatural-spinoff-rob-thomas-izombie-675484 |archive-date=2014-03-01 |language=en-US}}</ref>。2014年5月8日，CW電視網正式預定《閃電俠》整季，初步設想為13集<ref name="PickUp">{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2014/05/08/the-cw-new-series-fall-2014-the-flash/ |title=Fall TV Scoop: The CW Orders Four Dramas, Including Flash, iZombie and Jane the Virgin, Passes on Supernatural Spin-Off |last=Ausiello |first=Michael |website=TV Line |date=2014-05-08 |access-date=2014-05-08 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140508223350/http://tvline.com/2014/05/08/the-cw-new-series-fall-2014-the-flash/ |archive-date=2014-05-08 |language=en-US}}</ref>。2014年9月，CW電視網增加預訂3集<ref name="Deadline3">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2014/09/the-flash-jane-the-virgin-additional-scripts-cw-838768/ |title=CW's 'The Flash' & 'Jane The Virgin' Get Backup Script Orders Ahead Of Premieres |work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |date=2014-09-23 |access-date=2014-09-24 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140925082725/http://deadline.com/2014/09/the-flash-jane-the-virgin-additional-scripts-cw-838768/ |archive-date=2014-09-25 |language=en-US}}</ref>。2014年10月21日，CW最終補充預訂10集，第一季共23集<ref name="S1SeasonOrder">{{cite web|url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/10/21/the-flash-full-season/ |title='The Flash' gets full season ('Jane the Virgin' too) |last=Hibberd |first=James |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2014-10-21 |access-date=2014-10-21 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022000218/http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/10/21/the-flash-full-season/ |archive-date=2014-10-22 |language=en-US}}</ref>。

2014年7月，傑夫·強斯稱影集「至今最還原漫畫的改編作品，同時為[[星辰實驗室|星辰實驗室]]完善新的背景故事<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tvguide.com/News/Flash-Wentworth-Miller-Arrow-Crossovers-1084633.aspx |title=The Flash Casts Wentworth Miller, Plots Arrow Crossovers |last=Abram |first=Natalie |work=TV Guide |date=2014-07-18 |access-date=2014-07-18 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140720034146/http://www.tvguide.com/News/Flash-Wentworth-Miller-Arrow-Crossovers-1084633.aspx |archive-date=2014-07-20 |language=en-US}}</ref>。」2014年10月，傑夫·強斯稱不同於[[漫威影業|漫威影業]]的[[漫威電影宇宙|漫威電影宇宙]]，DC影業計劃將[[DC擴展宇宙|DC擴展宇宙]]與電視劇系列以多元宇宙的方式分離<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/jarettwieselman/the-man-at-the-center-of-dcs-tv-multiverse |title=The Man At The Center Of DC’s TV Multiverse |last=Wieselman |first=Jarett |work=BuzzFeed |date=2014-10-23 |access-date=2014-10-30 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ThkHPioZ?url=http://www.buzzfeed.com/jarettwieselman/the-man-at-the-center-of-dcs-tv-multiverse |archive-date=2014-10-30 |language=en-US}}</ref>。

