tle=Arrow preview: Who is Oliver Queen? |last=Abrams |first=Natalie |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2015-05-06 |access-date=2015-05-07 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150509003618/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/05/06/arrow-season-3-oliver-identity |archive-date=2015-05-09 |language=en-US}}</ref>。

